{"tid":2231643,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"想問大家用咩買電子書","createTime":"2020-10-05T20:59:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T14:44:47.000Z","uid":313435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c71426f9c2ed25c13153209aa298194e13d5910c","tid":2231643,"uid":313435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T20:59:38.000Z","msg":"想買konosuba小說 但土地問題 <br />\n可能要買電子書<br />\n未買過 淨係聽過book Walker <br />\n有冇ching有啲咩網推薦下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d0bb12e4993c93efabf76569c50c432db5a8ef0","tid":2231643,"uid":20554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T21:30:43.000Z","msg":"用緊kobo"},{"pid":"82f66a34804f429d457675f4b00aac22c39cfbaf","tid":2231643,"uid":252920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T21:51:19.000Z","msg":"kobo"},{"pid":"af4707007b9fbe800c76a8fe3a27dd0890359409","tid":2231643,"uid":209738,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T22:18:06.000Z","msg":"我用緊Kobo H2o Libra,$1699, 8GB版本<br />\n15日前在旺角豐澤買的，那裡有實體機試用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/79GwMYz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F79GwMYz.jpg&h=008e5201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我買Kobo H2o Libra的原因是為了它的實體鍵&mdash;&mdash;主要用來翻書的下一頁或上一頁。<br />\n其次，它的重量丶螢幕大小和價格都在我滿意的範圍， 我經常在大便的時候單手握住它來看小說和漫畫。<br />\n它唯一的缺點就是看漫畫的字有時太細但又不能教大一點，可惜螢幕尺寸再大一點的型號又太貴我又負擔不起<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39b59f6c387eac94cea4e1083ba9c59274d32a3","tid":2231643,"uid":144773,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T22:25:56.000Z","msg":"新手 唔明同用手機睇有咩分別"},{"pid":"a37e41073d0a8a40ef2d57ef35ecc05983db55b6","tid":2231643,"uid":68132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T22:51:59.000Z","msg":"箍煲"},{"pid":"a38208d332b05d9f360540af1e3840ba38accbaa","tid":2231643,"uid":244242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f39b59f6c387eac94cea4e1083ba9c59274d32a3","tid":2231643,"uid":144773,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T22:25:56.000Z","msg":"新手 唔明同用手機睇有咩分別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T22:54:02.000Z","msg":"個人睇得舒服啲<br />\n哩個既話無藍光 好似真係睇書咁 隻眼負擔小好多"},{"pid":"9c8ccf247f943a7f9b28381423a1e36f5ae19118","tid":2231643,"uid":343977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f39b59f6c387eac94cea4e1083ba9c59274d32a3","tid":2231643,"uid":144773,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T22:25:56.000Z","msg":"新手 唔明同用手機睇有咩分別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T23:42:25.000Z","msg":"睇過你就明"},{"pid":"392cc7b3f0c8287b505855bfa486a8dee0838e9b","tid":2231643,"uid":63282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T23:46:48.000Z","msg":"Kobo forma，八月買入，已經睇咗好幾本書了，開心使用中。"},{"pid":"715fa2b607beae7c4a66e0053b8b7b81aa841f9d","tid":2231643,"uid":186343,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T23:49:09.000Z","msg":"Kindle paper white+kobo買書落嚟轉格式<br />\n睇左50本書左右 開心使用中<br />\n幾舊水，2020買過最實用嘅產品"},{"pid":"298282b058a19578278da0f078392906bc529544","tid":2231643,"uid":243988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c71426f9c2ed25c13153209aa298194e13d5910c","tid":2231643,"uid":313435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T20:59:38.000Z","msg":"想買konosuba小說 但土地問題 <br />\n可能要買電子書<br />\n未買過 淨係聽過book Walker <br />\n有冇ching有啲咩網推薦下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T23:49:58.000Z","msg":"用電話/電話買"},{"pid":"3d9ac786a8c52a087eac85c7d9ef804f5a165cad","tid":2231643,"uid":45609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T23:50:24.000Z","msg":"未用過<br />\n想問下睇唔睇到google play買嘅書"},{"pid":"b87c5bb9ae5f1b62535f50def8fb9264790c401f","tid":2231643,"uid":102081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"715fa2b607beae7c4a66e0053b8b7b81aa841f9d","tid":2231643,"uid":186343,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"reply